# AXIOM — Navigo Mission
**Type:** Navido Mission File
**Concept:** AXIOM — Primary Working Platform
**Device:** Ubuntu Laptop
**Prime Frequency:** 2 (seed prime — the first, the origin)
**Status:** Initializing — user created, environment loading
